{"type":"message","id":"8c66e084","parentId":"d3be4085","timestamp":"2026-05-13T02:06:35.084Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script has syntax errors. Let me look at the script to understand what's wrong.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"脚本有语法错误，让我看看内容修一下。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VAEaPDS6jwGTASpARtx83719","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\tools\\hotupdate-scripts\\UpdateTestServer.ps1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":449,"output":94,"cacheRead":19328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19871,"cost":{"input":0.00006286,"output":0.000026320000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000541184,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000630364}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778637993762,"responseId":"c4e07694-53dd-41a5-9271-9265468ae422"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c73d7cab","parentId":"8c66e084","timestamp":"2026-05-13T02:06:35.094Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_VAEaPDS6jwGTASpARtx83719","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# UpdateTestServer.ps1 - 更新测试服\n# 流程: 关闭Unity → git pull → Unity 热更流水线(打资源+上传CDN)\n#\n# 使用方法:\n#   powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File \"路径\\UpdateTestServer.ps1\"\n#\n# 注意: 需要在 Unity Editor 中先配置好 BuildPipelineConfig.bytes 中的\"热更\"流水线步骤\n\nparam()\n\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\n\n# ===== 配置 =====\n$RepoRoot = \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\"\n$UnityProj = Join-Path $RepoRoot \"client\\cardv\"\n$UnityProcessName = \"Unity\"\n$UnityExe = \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity\\Hub\\Editor\\2020.3.49f1c1\\Editor\\Unity.exe\"\n$LogFile = Join-Path $UnityProj \"BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\"\n\nWrite-Host \"========================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"  更新测试服 - 开始\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"========================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# ===== Step 0: 关闭 Unity 编辑器 =====\nWrite-Host \"[Step 0/3] 关闭 Unity 编辑器...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\n$unityProcs = Get-Process -Name $UnityProcessName -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($unityProcs) {\n    $count = ($unityProcs | Measure-Object).Count\n    Write-Host \"  发现 $count 个 Unity 进程正在运行，正在关闭...\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n    $unityProcs | Stop-Process -Force\n    Write-Host \"  ✓ Unity 编辑器已关闭\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"  - Unity 编辑器未运行，跳过\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n}\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# ===== Step 1: Git Pull =====\nWrite-Host \"[Step 1/3] Git Pull - 更新当前分支...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\nif (!(Test-Path $RepoRoot)) {\n    Write-Error \"仓库路径不存在: $RepoRoot\"\n    exit 1\n}\n\nSet-Location $RepoRoot\nWrite-Host \"  仓库路径: $RepoRoot\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n\n# 检查是否在 git 仓库中\n$gitDir = Join-Path $RepoRoot \".git\"\nif (!(Test-Path $gitDir)) {\n    Write-Error \"该目录不是 Git 仓库\"\n    exit 1\n}\n\n# 获取当前分支名\n$currentBranch = & git rev-parse --abbrev-ref HEAD 2>$null\nif ($LASTEXITCODE -ne 0) {\n    Write-Error \"获取分支失败，请检查 git 安装\"\n    exit 1\n}\nWrite-Host \"  当前分支: $currentBranch\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n\n# 执行 git pull\nWrite-Host \"  执行 git pull ...\"\n& git pull 2>&1 | ForEach-Object { Write-Host \"    $_\" -ForegroundColor Gray }\nif ($LASTEXITCODE -ne 0) {\n    Write-Error \"git pull 失败，请手动解决冲突\"\n    exit 1\n}\nWrite-Host \"  ✓ Git Pull 完成\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\n# ===== Step 2: Unity 热更流水线(打资源+上传CDN) =====\nWrite-Host \"[Step 2/3] Unity 热更流水线(打资源+上传CDN)...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\nif (!(Test-Path $UnityExe)) {\n    Write-Error \"Unity 编辑器不存在: $UnityExe\"\n    exit 1\n}\nif (!(Test-Path $UnityProj)) {\n    Write-Error \"Unity 工程不存在: $UnityProj\"\n    exit 1\n}\n\n# 删除旧的日志文件\nif (Test-Path $LogFile) {\n    Remove-Item $LogFile -Force\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"  Unity 路径: $UnityExe\" -ForegroundColor Gray\nWrite-Host \"  工程路径: $UnityProj\" -ForegroundColor Gray\nWrite-Host \"  日志文件: $LogFile\" -ForegroundColor Gray\nWrite-Host \"  执行流水线: 热更(全部有效步骤)...\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n\n# 执行 Unity 批处理模式\n$proc = Start-Process -FilePath $UnityExe -ArgumentList @(\n    \"-batchmode\",\n    \"-quit\",\n    \"-nographics\",\n    \"-projectPath\", \"`\"$UnityProj`\"\",\n    \"-executeMethod\", \"YYZY.BuildPipeline.BuildPipeline.RunHotUpdatePipeline\",\n    \"-logFile\", \"`\"$LogFile`\"\"\n) -NoNewWindow -Wait -PassThru\n\n$exitCode = $proc.ExitCode\n\nif (Test-Path $LogFile) {\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"  === 日志摘要 (最后 20 行) ===\" -ForegroundColor Magenta\n    Get-Content $LogFile -Tail 20 | ForEach-Object { Write-Host \"    $_\" -ForegroundColor Gray }\n    Write-Host \"  =================================\" -ForegroundColor Magenta\n}\n\nif ($exitCode -eq 0) {\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"  ✓ Unity 热更流水线执行成功\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"  ✗ Unity 退出码: $exitCode (可能有错误，请查看日志)\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    exit $exitCode\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"========================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"  更新测试服 - 完成\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"========================================\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778637995093}}
{"type":"message","id":"4aab88cf","parentId":"c73d7cab","timestamp":"2026-05-13T02:06:42.047Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the syntax issues. Specifically:\n\n1. Line 34: `}` - The `param()` block at line 1 starts with `()` but doesn't have a closing `}`. Wait, that doesn't make sense. Let me re-look.\n\nActually `param()` at line 1 with empty parens is fine in PowerShell. The error says line 34 `}` is unexpected. Let me count lines... `param()` should not have a `}`.\n\nActually I think there might be an encoding issue. Let me check the file more carefully. The `# ===== Step 0: 关闭 Unity 编辑器 =====` comment has Chinese characters that might be causing encoding issues with PowerShell's parser.\n\nLooking more carefully at the issue:\n\nLine 33-34:\n```\nparam()\n# ...\n```\nWait, after `param()` with empty parentheses, there's nothing weird. Let me look at lines around 33-34.\n\nActually looking at the error again:\n- Line 34: unexpected `}`\n- Line 100: unexpected `)` with `-NoNewWindow -Wait -PassThru`\n- Line 123: unterminated string with `\"` (the `Write-Host ...` with the cyan color)\n- Line 111: missing closing `}` for the if block\n\nThis looks like encoding corruption - possibly UTF-8 with BOM being read as something else, or carriage returns causing issues.\n\nLet me try checking the file encoding and see if there are hidden characters.\n\nActually, let me just try using the batch file instead that was mentioned in TOOLS.md:\n`E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat`\n\nOr let me try a different approach - run the steps manually. But first, let me fix the script.\n\nWait, let me check the file encoding first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"脚本有编码或语法问题，让我看看具体内容。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_8aWqkzcFWLmrsLHtvVp49485","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"Get-Content 'E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\tools\\hotupdate-script